{
  "page_title": "服务商代开发",
  "apis": [
    {
      "group_title": "分配在职成员的客户群",
      "api_name": "onjob_transfer",
      "method": "POST",
      "api_url": "https://qyapi.weixin.qq.com/cgi-bin/externalcontact/groupchat/onjob_transfer",
      "description": "企业可通过此接口，将在职成员为群主的群，分配给另一个客服成员。",
      "query_params": [
        {
          "name": "access_token",
          "type": "string",
          "required": true,
          "description": "调用接口凭证"
        }
      ],
      "body_params": [
        {
          "name": "chat_id_list",
          "type": "array",
          "required": true,
          "description": "需要转群主的客户群ID列表。取值范围： 1 ~ 100"
        },
        {
          "name": "new_owner",
          "type": "string",
          "required": true,
          "description": "新群主ID"
        }
      ],
      "response_params": [
        {
          "name": "errcode",
          "type": "int32",
          "required": false,
          "description": "返回码"
        },
        {
          "name": "errmsg",
          "type": "string",
          "required": false,
          "description": "对返回码的文本描述内容"
        },
        {
          "name": "failed_chat_list",
          "type": "array",
          "required": false,
          "description": "没能成功继承的群"
        },
        {
          "name": "failed_chat_list.chat_id",
          "type": "string",
          "required": false,
          "description": "没能成功继承的群ID"
        },
        {
          "name": "failed_chat_list.errcode",
          "type": "int32",
          "required": false,
          "description": "没能成功继承的群，错误码"
        },
        {
          "name": "failed_chat_list.errmsg",
          "type": "string",
          "required": false,
          "description": "没能成功继承的群，错误描述"
        }
      ],
      "request_examples": [
        {
          "title": "示例",
          "language": "json",
          "code": "{\n    \"chat_id_list\" : [\"wrOgQhDgAAcwMTB7YmDkbeBsgT_AAAA\", \"wrOgQhDgAAMYQiS5ol9G7gK9JVQUAAAA\"],\n    \"new_owner\" : \"zhangsan\"\n}"
        }
      ],
      "response_examples": [
        {
          "title": "示例",
          "language": "json",
          "code": "{\n\t\"errcode\": 0,\n\t\"errmsg\": \"ok\",\n\t\"failed_chat_list\": [\n\t\t{\n\t\t\t\"chat_id\": \"wrOgQhDgAAcwMTB7YmDkbeBsgT_KAAAA\",\n\t\t\t\"errcode\": 90501,\n\t\t\t\"errmsg\": \"chat is not external group chat\"\n\t\t}\n\t]\n}"
        }
      ],
      "sections": [
        {
          "title": "注意",
          "content": "1. 继承给的新群主，必须是配置了客户联系功能的成员\n2. 继承给的新群主，必须有设置实名\n3. 继承给的新群主，必须有激活企业微信\n4. 同一个人的群，限制每天最多分配300个给新群主\n5. 继承给的新群主和旧的群主，需要在最近一年内至少登陆过一次企业微信\n为保障客户服务体验，90个自然日内，在职成员的每个客户群仅可被转接2次。"
        },
        {
          "title": "权限说明",
          "content": "企业需要使用配置到“可调用应用”列表中的自建应用secret所获取的accesstoken来调用。第三方应用需拥有“企业客户权限->客户联系->分配在职成员的客户群”权限。对于第三方/自建应用，群主必须在应用的可见范围。"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}